profile:
Pop-A-Lock of Simcoe County serves the communities of Barrie, Orillia, Collingwood, and surrounding areas. Please call us if you reside in other areas of the Central Ontario region like Gravenhurst, Huntsville & Parry Sound based on our availability. We are a 24/7 locksmith & security professional mobile service. It is as easy as searching for "find a locksmith near me" or Locksmith Barrie, Locksmith Orillia or Locksmith Collingwood to get immediate help. Our services include Emergency lockouts, Residential re-keying, installation & repair of locks and deadbolts, Commercial Re-keying, Master Key systems, high security locks, access control, door closers and general installation & repair of locking hardware. 

Pop-A-Lock Simcoe County is a certified auto locksmith specialist trained to provide automotive car door unlocking, ignition repair, key extraction, transponder, chip and smart key making and duplicating. Includes any type of key less remotes and fobs. We offer free quotes. As a CAA member, you are entitled to locksmith services benefits.
